OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FA former police officer and father-of-
OL,7,Ftwo who had sex with a vulnerable
OL,8,Fwoman while on duty has been jailed.
OL,10,FShamraze Arshad, who worked as a
OL,11,FGreater Manchester Police (GMP)
OL,12,Fofficer in Longsight, met the woman
OL,13,Fafter he and a fellow officer were
OL,14,Fcalled out to her student
OL,15,Faccommodation in south Manchester in
OL,16,FAutumn 2020.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
