OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FThe woman was reportedly suicidal, and
OL,7,FArshad submitted a care plan for her
OL,8,Fafter she was taken to hospital before
OL,9,Ffinishing his shift, Liverpool Crown
OL,10,FCourt heard.
OL,12,FJamie Baxter, prosecuting, told the
OL,13,Fcourt "that should have been the end
OL,14,Fof the matter", but later that
OL,15,Fmorning, Arshad used his police phone
OL,16,Fto find her personal details and
OL,17,Fcalled her just a few hours after she
OL,18,Fhad been taken to hospital.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
