OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FThe 38-year-old officer asked her to
OL,7,Fgo on a date, and eventually "began an
OL,8,Fintimate and ultimately sexual
OL,9,Frelationship with this vulnerable
OL,10,Fyoung woman whom he met in crisis".
OL,12,FArshad, from Bolton, has now been
OL,13,Fjailed for four years after being
OL,14,Ffound guilty of misconduct in public
OL,15,Foffice on Thursday 13 June.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
