OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FThe court heard how the investigation
OL,7,Fbegan in July 2021 after a routine
OL,8,Faudit check by GMP's Professional
OL,9,FStandards Directorate (PSD).JThe check
OL,10,Ffound Arshad had been using police
OL,11,Fsystems while off-duty and without a
OL,12,Fpolicing purpose. The probe then
OL,13,Frevealed he had been 'making a large
OL,14,Fvolume of contact' with a particular
OL,15,Fnumber from his work phone.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/11
