OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FThe woman described the relationship
OL,7,Fas being a "friends with benefits"
OL,8,Fsituation, in which he would would
OL,9,Fcome round for 15 to 20 minutes for a
OL,10,F"fun time in bed". She ended the
OL,11,Frelationship after seven months.
OL,13,FArshad was then arrested and suspended
OL,14,Fon 19 July 2021 and released on bail
OL,15,Fon condition not to contact the woman
OL,16,Fin any way - but he immediately went
OL,17,Fto her home and woke her by banging on
OL,18,Fher window.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
