OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FThe frightened woman hid in the
OL,7,Fbathroom and called the police. He was
OL,8,Farrested the following day for
OL,9,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,10,Fjustice and later charged.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, Arshad denied ever
OL,13,Fhaving sex with the woman.
OL,15,FThe jury of three women and nine men
OL,16,Ftook just 75 minutes to find him
OL,17,Fguilty. He shook his head and
OL,18,Frepeatedly muttered 'oh my god' as
OL,19,Ftheir verdict was delivered in court.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
