OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FArshad was also convicted of
OL,7,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,8,Fjustice and unauthorised access to the
OL,9,Fpolice computer at a trial last summer.
OL,11,FThe jury was unable to reach a verdict
OL,12,Fon the misconduct offence leading to a
OL,13,Fre-trial.
OL,15,FFollowing his four-year prison
OL,16,Fsentence on 14 June 2024, bosses at
OL,17,FGreater Manchester Police's have
OL,18,Fdescribed him as a 'disgrace to the
OL,19,Fpolice service'.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
