OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,FArshad was sacked from the force in
OL,7,FJanuary 2024, and police chiefs will
OL,8,Fnow write to the Deputy Mayor of
OL,9,FGreater Manchester to ask that he
OL,10,Floses his police pension.
OL,12,FFollowing his sentencing, Detective
OL,13,FChief Inspector Dave Jones, of GMP's
OL,14,FProfessional Standards Directorate,
OL,15,Fsaid: "I want to thank the courageous
OL,16,Fwoman in this case for providing us
OL,17,Fwith the evidence that was so
OL,18,Fimportant in ensuring that Arshad is
OL,19,Frightly held accountable for the full
OL,20,Fextent of his crimes.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
