OL,6,F"He abused his position as a police
OL,7,Fofficer to pursue a sexual
OL,8,Frelationship with a vulnerable woman
OL,9,Fwho he was supposed to protect in her
OL,10,Ftime of need.J"This is an unforgivable
OL,11,Fbreach of policing standards and it's
OL,12,Fright he will never be trusted to wear
OL,13,Fa police uniform again.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
