OL,3,CPolice officer labelled 'disgrace' for
OL,4,Chaving sex with woman on duty
OL,6,F"Arshad's jail term is fully deserved.
OL,7,FHe is a disgrace to the police service
OL,8,Fand does not represent the thousands
OL,9,Fof professional, honest, hard-working
OL,10,Fpolice officers across Greater
OL,11,FManchester who continue to protect the
OL,12,Fpublic each and every day.J"As soon as
OL,13,Fwe were legally able to, we sacked
OL,14,FArshad and, now that criminal
OL,15,Fproceedings have been concluded, we
OL,16,Fwill invite the Deputy Mayor to strip
OL,17,Fhim of his police pension."
